---
title: Mexican-Style Cheddar Beef & Garlic Rice with Charred Corn Slaw & Enchilada Sauce
description: We’re spicing up the table with this easy Mexican-style beef, spiced just the way you like it. Crank it up a notch with aromatic garlic rice and a charred corn slaw. It’s sure to be a party in your mouth tonight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65e92a20bbb0ffe7102d1efa-5338e1f4.jpeg
